snippet.title: MotoGP 17 - 2017 Season Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
The 2017 edition of the official MotoGP™ video game brings all the adrenaline and need for speed of the new world championship, including all the riders, teams and tracks of the 2017 season, and the Red Bull MotoGP™ Rookies Cup. 

http://motogpvideogame.com/
